lass=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6399023\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6399023\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 12, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kin1709198869557.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kin1709198869557.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kin1709198869557.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kin1709198869557\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxswitch</code> widget is a toggle field control. It always contains a\n\t\tfield value, even if it is not a valid Boolean. Unlike the checkbox widget, the\n\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">uxswitch</code> widget does not provide the indeterminate state, so null value\n\t\tor empty (\"\") value results in a format error.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kin1709198869557__section_pyy_dlm_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d313186e55\">Default Logical Widgets</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The default logical widget is <code class=\"ph codeph\">ux-Switch</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kin1709198869557__section_knr_dlm_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d313186e67\">Triggers</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">(web)trigger onchange</code>: This trigger is fired when the\n\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">uxswitch</code> value is changed. </p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kin1709198869557__section_qsx_clm_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d313186e81\">Extends fluent-switch Web Component</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">This widget is implemented using the Fluent web component fluent-switch. Most of its features\n\t\t\t\tare also available in this widget. Most of its events are mapped to triggers. For\n\t\t\t\tmore information, see the Fluent documentation on the fluent-switch web\n\t\t\t\tcomponent.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kin1709198869557__section_ic2_dg2_q1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d313186e90\">Keyboard support</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">When widget has focus, pressing the <kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Spacebar</kbd> key toggles the\n\t\t\t\twidget state.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kin1709198869557__section_inh_lqh_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d313186e102\">Layout processing</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Widget class method <code class=\"ph codeph\">processLayout()</code> constructs the template HTML for this\n\t\t\t\twidget. It generates nodes for the control itself as well as slots for label,\n\t\t\t\tchecked-message, unchecked-message and error icon, and returns it to Uniface. Use\n\t\t\t\tthis function to enhance the widget with more static features.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kin1709198869557__section_hf4_frh_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d313186e115\">Widget properties</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxswitch</code> widget supports the following properties:<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Widget Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Property</strong></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:title</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines a hover over text or tooltip, currently used as\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thelper text.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:disabled</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the widget as being disabled.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:readonly</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the widget as being read-only.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:hidden</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines a boolean value that hides or shows a switch.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:tabindex</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Allows or prevents a field from getting sequential focus\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tusually with the Tab key.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">class:classname</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Boolean value that adds or removes a specified class.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">label-text</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the label text.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">label-position</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Defines the position of the label with respect to its widget.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe available options are:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kin1709198869557__ul_v1w_bg1_fdc\">\n<li class=\"li\">before (default)</li>\n<li class=\"li\">after</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"kin1709198869557__note_chl_dg1_fdc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If the <code class=\"ph codeph\">label-position</code> is not defined for the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twidget, it is aligned by default before the widget.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">unchecked-message</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines a message for an unchecked state.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">checked-message</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines a message for a checked state.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">exclude</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"kin1709198869557__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines that there will be no column for the field in the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">uxdatagrid</code>.<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"kin1709198869557__note_uhf_fnn_tcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tis actually not a widget property. It is a field property,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tused by the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxdatagrid</code> widget if that is\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe containing entity's widget.</div></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kin1709198869557__section_yvb_hdn_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d313186e293\">Helper and validation error visualization</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">A <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxswitch</code> deals with the following error visualizations:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kin1709198869557__ul_jqz_cfl_q1c\">\n<li class=\"li\">Red color border and outline alert</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Alert icon </li>\n<li class=\"li\">Tool-tip when hovering the alert icon showing the error message</li>\n<li class=\"li\">When the widget is in an error state, the checked/unchecked message slot is\n\t\t\t\t\t\tchanged to display the invalid state. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">By toggling the error is resolved. The error is not brought back by toggling\n\t\t\t\t\t\tback. </li>\n</ul></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kin1709198869557__section_vnb_ndn_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d313186e322\">UI blocking</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">When the field is in transaction, the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxswitch</code> widget blocks user\n\t\t\t\tinput by becoming read-only.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kin1709198869557__section_c4l_z4m_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d313186e334\">Widget styling</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"kin1709198869557__table_fmd_rjl_q1c_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"kin1709198869557__table_fmd_rjl_q1c_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"kin1709198869557__table_fmd_rjl_q1c\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\" id=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\" name=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\">CSS Selector</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\" id=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\" name=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\">Selected node(s)</label></div></div><div class=\"searchAllTable\"><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-all-smart-table\">Filter results...</label><input aria-label=\"Filter results in the table\" class=\"zDocsInputField\" id=\"search-all-smart-table\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><button aria-label=\"Submit\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldSearch\" type=\"submit\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-search\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-search\"></use></svg></button><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">23 rows found</div></div><div><button aria-label=\"Export table to a file\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageTableExportButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-v\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-v\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicPageTableExportMenu\"><button aria-label=\"Export to Excel\" class=\"dropdown-item\" type=\"button\">Export to Excel</button><button aria-label=\"Export to CSV\" class=\"dropdown-item\" type=\"button\">Export to CSV</button></div></div></div><div class=\"dataTables_scroll\" data-testid=\"sticky-header-table\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollHead\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; border: 0px; width: 100%;\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollHeadInner\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; width: 709px; padding-right: 0px;\"><table class=\"table dataTable no-footer\" count-columns=\"2\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; width: 709px;\"><caption></caption><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\"><th aria-controls=\"kin1709198869557__table_fmd_rjl_q1c\" aria-label=\"CSS Selector: activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" id=\"kin1709198869557__table_fmd_rjl_q1c__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 376.516px;\" tabin